{"tid":746511,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"馬會：港人每年投注外圍輸掉120億港元，可興建17,000 間公屋","createTime":"2018-07-17T15:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T14:52:02.000Z","uid":72795,"like":27,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"f2fb2651eac900538270b866d158341e31815114","tid":746511,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:04:29.000Z","msg":"希望大家拍硬檔，唔好賭外圍，幫政府起公屋　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n疊碼仔及非法賭博網站招攬顧客<br />\n非法賭博集團及中介人(又稱&rdquo;疊碼仔&rdquo;)在本港的活動越趨活躍，疊碼仔不但提供借貸等利誘賭博人士，更贈送船票及酒店住宿吸引港人到賭場及賭船賭博；賭博集團更推出越來越多積分和優惠計劃吸引新客戶，尤其是年青客戶，當中衍生的社會問題，對本港構成嚴重威脅。<br />\n<br />\n非法賭博集團以利潤為大前提，利用借貸、種類繁多的投注方式等吸引顧客。非法賭博集團不論顧客年齡和經濟能力，鼓勵他們在輸錢後繼續投注以求回本，並提供非法借貸，導致他們欠債累累；非法賭博集團又提供二十四小時不停的投注機會，往往促使顧客快速、連續地投注，容易導致問題賭博。<br />\n<br />\n近年更因上網技術和速度大幅提升，以及智能手機、平板電腦等普及，令市民接觸非法賭博渠道的機會增加，專門追蹤網站使用率的調查便發現，每月有至少二十三萬名市民瀏覽或光顧非法賭博網站；<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">另據估算，港人每年因投注非法外圍而輸掉的投注達到120億港元，相當於政府「關愛基金」總額的60%，若果把這筆款項投放於本港社會建設，可興建17,000 間公屋、100所中學和接近300 間安老院舍。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n本港非法外圍賭博的投注額，已達到數千億港元，比合法博彩的投注額1500億港元高出一倍。非法賭博活動日益猖獗，引伸的連串社會問題和犯罪活動亦越趨嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkjc.com/responsible-gambling/ch/anti-illegal/index.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkjc.com%2Fresponsible-gambling%2Fch%2Fanti-illegal%2Findex.aspx&d=7f2ZIAzAuNvc8Kmrht0lycmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=fe02a896\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkjc.com/responsible-gambling/ch/anti-illegal/index.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"6b89b32937269b0524f0e026ea313bf6b0a8c7b7","tid":746511,"uid":156542,"like":144,"dislike":0,"score":144,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:08:57.000Z","msg":"戇鳩 <br />\n<br />\n狗會正垃圾"},{"pid":"cb7f49378774225826291d5a8beac8c8a09b945a","tid":746511,"uid":38030,"like":116,"dislike":2,"score":114,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:11:10.000Z","msg":"馬會其實無錢賺，只求打個和<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea8965468a1476b15f340ea2a4eb05d7d4efe29","tid":746511,"uid":168525,"like":112,"dislike":1,"score":111,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:13:32.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府每年浪費既錢夠起唔知幾多萬間公屋<br />\n<br />\n況且呢個垃圾政府就算有錢都唔會起足夠既公屋"},{"pid":"5db4000fd05b42fafe89786045f2b527aa8644b6","tid":746511,"uid":13503,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:14:34.000Z","msg":"狗會不思進取又唔諗下點解犯法都要賭外圍，日日選擇閪波黎開走地又低水"},{"pid":"66762bd8daca1f230bece7fc25853298de639f8a","tid":746511,"uid":37240,"like":84,"dislike":0,"score":84,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:15:36.000Z","msg":"馬會又知外圍投注額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"55d1af66f3ffc5f3f28dea62522d7034f773c43e","tid":746511,"uid":3647,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:17:07.000Z","msg":"馬會起公屋未"},{"pid":"49082bbaa57985982752be65270ebc67cf618af8","tid":746511,"uid":3122,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:20:29.000Z","msg":"estimate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750ae24ad821b09c63144329aa4e204270c67321","tid":746511,"uid":158613,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:21:22.000Z","msg":"膠鐵夠起幾多間？"},{"pid":"a886335fb5ab70f215ee2dbbc720a6c5931adbd4","tid":746511,"uid":76063,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:22:20.000Z","msg":"鬼叫你開價西 食水深咩"},{"pid":"d0cf8baa25aea10a6d37cf641874bf98fb872af2","tid":746511,"uid":37062,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:22:47.000Z","msg":"垃圾狗會 食水深學人講道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"